%header
  .video-container
    %video{autoplay: "", height: "auto", loop: "loop", muted: "muted", preload: "auto", width: "100%"}
      %source{:src => "https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/6564676/video.mp4", :type => "video/mp4"}
    .color
    .header-copy
      %h1 What's Your Type?
      %h4
        A 4-question Myers-Briggs personality quiz

    %p (scroll down to start)


#section
  .row
    .wrapper
      %h2 1) I tend to be...
      .button-wrapper
        .button1{:data => {:letter => "E"}} Extraverted
        %h4 I get energy by being with people
      .button-wrapper
        .button2{:data => {:letter => "I"}} Introverted
        %h4 I get energy from alone time

  .row
    .wrapper
      %h2 2) I am generally more...
      .button-wrapper
        .button1{:data => {:letter => "N"}} Abstract
        %h4 I am often up-in-the-clouds
      .button-wrapper
        .button2{:data => {:letter => "S"}} Concrete
        %h4 I am more down-to-earth

  .row
    .wrapper
      %h2 3) I usually make decisions based on...
      .button-wrapper
        .button1{:data => {:letter => "F"}} My gut
        %h4 I am more values-based <br> and view things as subjective
      .button-wrapper
        .button2{:data => {:letter => "T"}} Logic
        %h4 I am more principle-based <br> and view things as objective

  .row
    .wrapper
      %h2 4) I typically...
      .button-wrapper
        .button1{:data => {:letter => "J"}} Plan ahead
        %h4 I generally try and run my life
      .button-wrapper
        .button2{:data => {:letter => "P"}} Adapt as I go
        %h4 I generally like to let life happen

%section.your-type
  %h3 Well done! You're likely a...
  %h2
    %a{:target => "_blank", :class => "mbti-letters"}
  %p Click above to learn more

